channel.title: Contest - Free Giveaway[Deadline 4/1/11 to join signup]
channel.description:
I have permission from Newty to post this. _____________________________________ [center][size=24pt][b]Contest Giveaway[/b][/size][/center]
I have a black Nintendo Gameboy pocket and about 7 games I want to giveaway to the community. I will be shipping this to the winner for free, no charge at all. [b][u]ONLY IF YOU ARE WITH IN US TERRITORY[/u][/b]
In order to get a chance to win the contest, you must post a comment saying you want in. [s]I will allow 30 members maximum to join the raffle. When all members have joined[/s]. I will now allow as many members, but until 4/1/11, that's my deadline for members to join.You can guess a number from 1-100, and the person who gets the exact/closest to the number will win. I will use http://random.org/ to generate the random number.
I will post pictures up tomorrow, i'm tired and the items are upstairs. They all work fantastic though.
Good luck :D
